summary: If You Must Leave
title: If You Must Leave
body:
Fandom : Marvel

In English, by camwolf, Rated K

Synopsis : Sarah Rogers and Winifred Barnes learn early on that there’s no point in trying to keep their sons away from each other. Not that they’d try. 
The lives of Steve Rogers and Bucky Barnes, as seen through the eyes of their mothers.

Pairing : Steve Rogers/Bucky Barnes

1 chapter, Complete -> here 

Why do I recommend it : I didn’t think I would love this story this much. This fanfiction is a very heartful piece narrating Bucky and Steve’s childhood in Brooklyn, until their departure to the war. The points of view privileged are those of their mothers, Sarah and Winifred. Their dilemmas are put in relief and we discover their fight against poverty and illness. And to be perfectly honest, Bucky and Steve are really cute but also a handfull ! The result is warm, full of feelings and really well written.
And this end ! The last part is amazing, so right and piercing. Go read it !

summary:
MCU Moodboard
MJ knows about Spider-Man, but Peter doesn't know she does. MJ is just waiting for Peter to give up and tell her,...
body:
MCU Moodboard

MJ knows about Spider-Man, but Peter doesn’t know she does. MJ is just waiting for Peter to give up and tell her, and she uses every method possible. She is unhelpful when they play Portal together, she’s even more of a dick to him, and she uses every meme possible to piss him off. Even when Peter confesses his love to her, she keeps friendzoning him, trying to get him to crack. It drives them both insane, because they both want to be with each other. In the end, MJ gives up and tells Peter she knows. Peter gets upset, because he had been wanting to tell her for a very long time, but he understands that the more people who know his true identity, the more likely it is that villains will target them. He doesn’t want the people he loves to suffer because of him. It’s bad enough that Ned and May know. MJ ruffles his hair and flips him off. Like any villain could handle her? Ten minutes after taking her as a hostage and they would be kicking her out, crying their eyes out in terror. Nobody fucks with MJ; Peter’s proud of her.

——————

I take requests for MCU moodboards; any character, any AU, any ship… even NSFW!

Check out my other MCU Moodboards. You can request moodboards here. Thanks guys 😊 x

She is unhelpful when they play Portal together, she’s even more of a dick to him, and she uses every meme possible to piss him off. Even when Peter confesses his love to her, she keeps friendzoning him, trying to get him to crack. It drives them both insane, because they both want to be with each other. In the end, MJ gives up and tells Peter she knows. Peter gets upset, because he had been wanting to tell her for a very long time, but he understands that the more people who know his true identity, the more likely it is that villains will target them. He doesn’t want the people he loves to suffer because of him. It’s bad enough that Ned and May know. MJ ruffles his hair and flips him off. Like any villain could handle her? Ten minutes after taking her as a hostage and they would be kicking her out, crying their eyes out in terror. Nobody fucks with MJ; Peter’s proud of her.
